Description: SeaBird Exploration PLC is a Norway-based company engaged in the oil and gas industry. The Company specializes in the provision of surveying services, including two-dimensional (2D), source, ocean bottom seismic and shallow water three-dimensional (3D) studies. It provides contract seismic surveys, as well as operates in the multi-client sector, offering a data library, which covers the region of Australia, Hebrides, Norway and Philippines. Its multi-client surveys are also performed in the cooperation with Searcher Seismic and GeoPartners. Furthermore, the Company operates worldwide through a number of subsidiaries, such as Munin Navigation Company Limited, SeaBird Exploration FZ-LLC, GeoBird Management AS, SeaBird Exploration Americas Inc and Baruka Management Limited.
